    <ul>
FEDERAL
<p>
    <li><a href=#aa1>DOLE: "Just Cut Out the Advertising"</a></li>
<p>LOCAL
<p>
    <li><a href=#aa2>WA: Teens to Protest Ticketmaster/Joe Camel Promotion</a></li>
