<li>11/7/96 <a href="http://www.nydailynews.com/most/NEWS/110796/PUBLIC_F/4670.htm"> Why Didn't Bill Attack Dole's Character?</a> Of all people to criticize Dole's tobacco connection--Sidney Zion!. NY Daily News
<li>11/7/96 <a href="http://www2.phillynews.com:80/inquirer/96/Nov/07/business/STOX07.htm"> Tobacco Stocks Shoot Up on Republican House Win</a> Philadelphia Inquirer
<li>11/7/96<a href="http://167.8.29.8/plweb-cgi/idoc.pl?395+unix+_free_user_+www.usatoday.com..80+USATODAY_ONLINE+USATODAY_ONLINE+NEWS+NEWS++smoking"> Tobacco Was Dad's Life--It Also Took His Life</a> <b>Victor Crawford Jr. Speaks!</b> USA Today
