<li>11/8/96<a href="http://interactive3.wsj.com/edition/current/articles/SB84740793929246000.htm"> A Catalog of Horrors</a> The Brooks Brothers' catalog?? Yes, BB: <i>Yet in  keeping with the latest fad of these moronic times, the Brooks Brothers  catalog puts a cigar in just about everyone's hands. And gives to the  smokers expressions of half-in-the-bag self-satisfaction, like  Pinnochio's jackass friends on Pleasure Island. </i> WSJ
<li>11/8/96<a href="http://www2.nando.net:80/newsroom/ntn/nation/110896/nation10_1816_S1.html"> RJR linked tobacco to cancer in 1953--Report</a> Nando Net
<li>11/8/96<a href="http://www2.nando.net:80/newsroom/ntn/world/110896/world8_4738.html"> Turkish Parliament Bans Smoking in Most Public Places </a> Nando Net

<li>11/09/96<a href="http://www.kcstar.com/sbin/iarecord?NS-doc-path=/vol1/pubs/stage/local/30d907ac.b09&NS-doc-offset=1&NS-collection=Local&NS-search-set=/var/tmp/328ba/aaaa003lw8ba48a&"> Gere Covert vs. Shook Hardy Bacon</a> Death, revenge and high-priced lawyers. The Louisiana Jane Covert tobacco liability trial, expertly and richly covered by Matthew Schofield of the<a href="http://www.kcstar.com "> Kansas City Star.</a> Here's the 11/11<a href="http://www.kcstar.com/sbin/iarecord?NS-doc-path=/vol1/pubs/stage/local/30d90820.b11&NS-doc-offset=0&NS-collection=Local&NS-search-set=/var/tmp/328ba/aaaa003lw8ba48a&"> follow-up</a>
<li>11/11/96 <a href="http://yourhealthdaily.com:80/316_111196_112212_18851.html"> Smoking Hinders Infertility Treatment </a> Your Health Daily
<li>11/11/96<a href="http://152.160.1.36:80/1996/menu/stories/74238.htm"> Children from Smoking Homes Need More Oxygen Therapy After Surgery: Study</a> Detroit News
