couver. Article is from the brand-new website of RJR's (and Bowman Gray's) home town paper, the Winston-Salem Journal. (Thanks, RD)<li>02/09/97 <a href="http://www.nando.net/newsroom/nao/nc/020997/nc11_29080.html"> Tobacco Funded Smoke Study Spurs Debate on Objectivity</a> Raleigh News & Observer<HR><address><br>***********************   <li>©1997 <a href=mailto:geneb@dx.com>Gene Borio,</a> Tobacco BBS (212-982-4645). WebPage: <a href=" http://www.tobacco.org">  http://www.tobacco.org).</a>Original Tobacco BBS material may be reprinted in any non-commercial venue if accompanied by this credit </li> </address><br>***********************<br><a href=http://www.tobacco.org>Return to Tobacco BBS HomePage</a><br>***********************<p>END OF DOCUMENT</p></HTML>
