<META NAME="copyright" content="Copyight 1996 Mealey Publications; Posted with permission by Gene Borio, Tobacco BBS (212-982-4645; WebPage: http://www.tobacco.org.) Original material may be reprinted in any non-commercial venue as long as it is accompanied by this notice.">
