<center><h3>Alert!</center></h3>
<strong>A live, Internet ISDN online broadcast featuring Stanton Glantz, author of <a href="Resources/cigpprs.html">The Cigarette Papers,</a> will be held on Friday, May 17, 1996 from 6-8PM PDT </strong> (that's 9-11 PM EST for us East-Coasters)
<br>The event is Dr. Glantz's appearance at the Printers Inc. Bookstore (Palo Alto, CA; 6PM to 8PM PDT). The broadcast will cover the discussion at the store, after which Glantz will answer radio call-in questions during a live show on KFJC (89.7 FM, Los Altos Hills) which will be broadcast over the Internet with RealAudio.

<p>The Website for accessing the show is still to be determined; updates and software/modem requirements may be found at the <a href=" http://www.pibooks.com/glantz.html"> Printers Inc. Website</a>
