<h2><center>Tobacco-Related Internet Resources
</center></h2><P>

FEDERAL LAWS WHICH EXEMPT CIGARETTES:
<ul>
<li>Food, Drug & Cosmetic Act</li> 
<li>Consumer Product Safety Act</li> 
<li>Fair Packaging & Labeling Act</li> 
<li>Federal Hazardous Substances Act</li> 
</ul>
