Africa and the Discovery of America (1992)
Brooklyn; A & B Books

-----------------------------------------------------------------
Scott Cutlip
The Unseen Power
*a history of the PR industry. In addition to Bernays, it talks about John Hill's work setting up the Tobacco Institute in the 1950s.

