s, health, and activist sites.<li><A HREF = "http://www.cs.brown.edu/people/lsh/smoking.html">Smoking from All Sides Page </A>  <BR>A valiant attempt to provide links to everything--from whatever side--there is about tobacco on the net.</i></center></li><li>National Clearinghouse on Tobacco and Health's<a href="http://www.ccsh.ca/ncth/db/wre/bwwre.htm"> WebSite Rolodex</a></li><li><A href="http://www.autonomy.com/smoke.htm">The Master Anti-Smoking Page</a></li><li>QuitNet's <a href="http://www.quitnet.org/Library/Links/URL_Show.qry?Filter=Tobacco&Category=Media:Sources&Summaries=on&Recommended=on&ShowSearch=Off">News Sources Tobacco Links Page</a><li><A HREF= http://artitude.wwa.com:80/links.htm>"Links for those with Conscience and Consciousness"</A></li></ul><hr><h3><a name=aa3><center>Categories:</a></h3></center>  <ul>  <li><a href=#aa2>SITES OF THE MONTH:</a></li><p>  <li><a href=#aa4>TOBACCO CONTROL RESOURCES</a></li>    <ul>    <li><a href=#aa5>Regional</a></li>    <li><a href=#aa6>Health Organizations</a></li>    <li><a href=#aa7>Mighty Resources For Smokers Trying To Quit:</a></li>      <ul>      <li><a href=#aa8>Commercial Cessation Products Are in the <a href="http://www.tobacco.org/Misc/com.html"> COMMERCIAL SECTION</a></li>      </ul>    <li><a href=#aa9>Personal</a></li>    <li><a href=#aa10><a name = aarestaurant>Restaurant Guides</a></li>    </ul><p>  <li><a href=#aa11>MEDIA/NEWS RESOURCES</a></li>    <ul>    <li><a href=#aa12>News Articles</a></li>    <li><a href=#aa13>Miscellaneous Tobacco-oriented WebSites</a></li>    <li><a href=#aa14>Documents:</a></li>    <li><a href=#aa15>Statistics</a></li>    </ul><p>  <li><a href=#aa16>NEWSGROUPS</a></li>    <ul>      <li><a href=#aa17>Listservs</a></li>    </ul><p>  <li><a href=#aa18>TOBACCO SPINS ITS WEB</a></li>    <ul>    <li><a href=#aa19>Agriculture</a></li>    <li><a href=#aa20>Business</a></li>    <li><a href=#aa21>International</a></li>    <li><a href=#