http://nationalreview.com:80/nationalreview/clinton/real.html 204.71.237.85 19970114061610 text/html 5732
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 06:16:28 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 25-Nov-96 22:11:35 GMT
Content-length: 5548
