http://nationalreview.com:80/nationalreview/daybox.html 204.71.237.85 19970114061632 text/html 6885
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 06:16:54 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 00:03:09 GMT
