http://nationalreview.com:80/nationalreview/27jan97/rusty.html 204.71.237.85 19970114062222 text/html 5669
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 06:22:24 GMT
