<HTML>
<head>
<title>
National Review In Print
</title>
</head>
<BODY bgcolor=#ffffff>
<body>
<center><img src="inprint.gif" ALT="NATIONAL REVIEW in Print">
<hr width=50%>
<br>
<!------------------------------------------------------------------------>

<a href="/nationalreview/29july96/week.html">
<img src="/nationalreview/images/sweek.gif" ALT="The Week"></a>
<br>
 <a href="/nationalreview/29july96/feature.html">
<img src="/nationalreview/images/sfeature.gif" ALT="Feature Article"></a>
