<P>
<hr width=50%>
<H2> CORRECT</H2>
</CENTER>
<P>
<BR>
<blockquote>
<!------------------------------------------------------------>
<p>
Since Moscow is still willing to pay $14 million per day to continue to support Fidel Castro, Daniel Ortega reasonably hopes to hang on to that incremental Soviet subvention necessary to eliminate any possibility that the tatterdemalion contras will ever seriously challenge the Marxist <b>hegemony</b> in Nicaragua.
<P>
<center>(On the Right)</center>





